<plot>Two San Francisco detectives (Kelvin Han Yee, Tim Lounibos) discover a corpse in an abandoned car. From the dead man's wallet and a tape recorder, they determine the man (Sab Shimono) was a money launderer. The story is then told in flashback, narrated by the dead man. Seems he was being pursued after robbing a partner (Philip Kan Gotanda) who had been robbing him. Hiding out in a warehouse, he tries to re-establish contact with his children (Tamlyn Tomita, Greg Watanabe). In the warehouse, he then is contacted by a woman (Julia Nickson) who frequents it because her husband died there and becomes obsessed with its new inhabitant as teh reincarnate of her husband. Of course, following all of these goings-on, he ultimately must face down his pursuers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?335649</url></doc>
